title: David Lawrence’s cv
text:
Legal Intern \
Huhem Law Firm PLLC — Dallas, Texas \ July 2025 – September 2025

Identified a procedural gap during trial preparation by consulting opposing counsel post-hearing and recommended a documentation protocol, saving clients hundreds of dollars per case
Drafted and filed legal documents including eviction petitions, civil litigation petitions, demand letters, and legal memos
Represented firm’s clients in court as an agent, winning more than 90% of cases

title: David Lawrence’s cv
text:
Volunteer \
Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints — Abidjan, Côte d’Ivoire \ November 2021 – November 2023

Served as a full-time volunteer focusing on planning, goal setting, leadership, and creating service opportunities
Gained conversational and written fluency in French within six months by working daily with native speakers
Trained and supervised more than 20 volunteers by teaching French, cultural norms, and effective teaching techniques

title: David Lawrence’s cv
text:
Front Desk Receptionist \
DoubleTree by Hilton — Bloomington, Illinois \ April 2021 – October 2021

Solved problems under pressure, ensuring accurate payments and improving workflow, preventing major financial losses
Improved efficiency by optimizing guest records and proactively addressing special requests, saving an average of one hour during rush periods
Provided exceptional service by fulfilling custom client requests beyond standard job duties
Elevated workplace appearance by consistently wearing a suit, inspiring coworkers to follow
